#: _versions/3.33/guides/grpc-generation-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Because of the packaging of `protoc` and the plugin (using classifier), it's not possible to exclude undesired platforms individually."
msgstr "由于 `protoc` 和插件（使用分类器）的封装方式，无法单独排除不需要的平台。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.33/guides/grpc-generation-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When using https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AArch64[AArch64] on macOS be aware of this https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/11844[issue]: meaning that the macOS https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86[x86_64] protoc and macOS aarch_64 protoc are the `same` - both are macOS x86_64. So you need to enable https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosetta_(software)[Rosetta] (`softwareupdate --install-rosetta`) on your ARM based macOS if you want to generate protobuf classes."
msgstr "在 macOS 上使用 link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/AArch64[AArch64] 时，请注意以下 link:https://github.com/grpc/grpc-java/issues/11844[问题] ：即 macOS link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86[x86_64] 版本的 protoc 和 macOS aarch_64 版本的 protoc 实际上是 `相同的` ——两者均为 macOS x86_64 版本。 因此，若要在基于 ARM 的 macOS 上生成 protobuf 类，您需要启用 link:https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rosetta_(software)[Rosetta] （执行命令 ` `softwareupdate --install-rosetta` `）。"

